  "text": "The mechanisms responsible for hypomagnesemia in association with anti-EGFR MoAbs have not been well defined. Increased EGFR expression in the ascending loop of Henle, where 70% of filtered magnesium is reabsorbed, may result in damage to the renal tubule and interfere with magnesium transport [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
